message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which holds significant value to both of us. Given its worth to you, I believe it's important to offer a fair deal. I propose to sell the product to you for $9500. This price not only reflects the value the product holds for you but also ensures a reasonable profit margin for me. I am confident this offer will meet our mutual expectations and facilitate a successful transaction. Please let me know if you require any further information or have questions about the product.
